  abstract    = {An Individual Patient Data (IPD) meta-analysis is often considered
	the gold-standard for synthesising survival data from clinical trials.
	An IPD meta-analysis can be achieved by either a two-stage or a one-stage
	approach, depending on whether the trials are analysed separately
