	interval, NNTB 5.0 to NNTB 8.4), 10.8 for oral diabetes drugs (NNTB
	8.1 to NNTB 15.0), 5.4 for orlistat (NNTB 4.1 to NNTB 7.6), and 4.0
	for jiangtang bushen (NNTH 16.9 to NNTB 24.8). CONCLUSIONS: Lifestyle
	and pharmacological interventions reduce the rate of progression
