  volume      = {27},
  abstract    = {Understanding length of stay for babies in neonatal care is vital
	for planning services and for counselling parents. While previous
	work has focused on the length of stay of babies who survive to discharge,
	when investigating resource use within neonatal care, it is important
	to also incorporate information on those babies who die while in
